{"tid":56798,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"艾薇兒臥病2年擊退「萊姆症」　宣告復出逼哭歌迷","createTime":"2016-12-27T13:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T13:51:27.000Z","uid":63501,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c130aee01d871d1c1609da535bb88c94557e867","tid":56798,"uid":63501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://star.ettoday.net/news/837449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F837449&d=QTcD7cvUk5BaeGQS6jHlGhpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=655a781c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://star.ettoday.net/news/837449</a><br />\n<br />\n「搖滾小天后」艾薇兒（Avril Lavigne）過去創造出許多經典歌曲，2年前卻無預警消失，直到2015年4月才出面證實自己得了「萊姆症」，必需好好調養身體，事隔1年多，突然在聖誕節當天於IG貼出大篇長文，宣布要回歸歌壇，讓大批粉絲興奮不已。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n艾薇兒先是感謝所有的粉絲在這2年的支持和耐心等候，「這段日子不只是與疾病奮鬥，同時也啟發了我，影響到我的音樂、生活、藝術和個性。之後會繼續用『艾薇兒基金會』持續關注萊姆病，並提供幫助。」同時宣布目前正在製作新的音樂作品，2017年將會推出新專輯，而她已經等不及想趕快分享這份喜悅，開心直呼：「希望你們會期待我的新歌，2017年肯定會是很棒的一年。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAvril<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返黎喇  幾鍾意佢d歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8ef35d86a925ab8f10007b0e652a78392cc83f","tid":56798,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"Hello kitty"},{"pid":"ab5155ccfdbbcef2325c4bcd622e7410d8c9f31f","tid":56798,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:46:31.000Z","msg":"Ka ka kawaii"},{"pid":"c4864afab18fc36de1d54f5acfbf6dd9d5220c98","tid":56798,"uid":61675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:49:00.000Z","msg":"當年中學雞已經開始聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df95adad47cbe767fcdfde1502b2369d0d5d659","tid":56798,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T13:51:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱先係fb見到<br />\n不過都係收檔啦 搞臭個朵<br />\n上隻碟得here's to never growing up 同let her go 聽到過"}]}